    "How do individuals construct and interact with a customizable chatbot powered by large language models (LLMs) for emotional support?",
    "What design opportunities could potentially enhance the customizability of LLM-powered chatbots in meeting individualized emotional needs?In this section, we describe the design rationales of ChatLab and its interface components.",
    "Note that we did not intend to evaluate ChatLab for its effectiveness in supporting individuals' emotional needs; instead, we aim to leverage it as part of the RtD approach to answer the above research questions.",
